            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_kCdfmD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every creation at TABASQUISHY® begins with an original spark — a story, a feeling, a moment of softness waiting to take shape.<br/>Our IP collection represents a new wave of designer toys: original, tactile, and full of cozy charm.<br/><br/>Each character is imagined and sculpted by our in-house team, blending the spirit of modern art toys with the handmade warmth that defines TABASQUISHY®. From sketch to finish, every curve and color carries the touch of our designers — proof that true creativity is meant to be felt.<br/><br/>We believe that design should be playful, comforting, and real.<br/>Through every squish, we hope to share the simple joy of creation — a soft, soothing world built from original ideas and heartfelt hands.</p>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        }
      },
